---
import { IconHeart, IconMessageCircle, IconX } from "../../icons/Icons";
---

<article
  class="w-96 bg-[#f7f9f9] dark:bg-[#16181C] p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col gap-3"
>
  <header class="w-full flex justify-between items-center gap-3">
    <aside class="flex gap-2">
      <img
        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full avatar"
        src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1685076669432758274/P2SW5cdz_200x200.jpg"
        loading="lazy"
        alt="Avatar de Humberto Yupanqui Apaza"
      />
      <div>
        <h5
          class="font-bold text-[15px] text-[#0F1419] dark:text-[#E7E9EA] line-clamp-1"
        >
          Humberto Yupanqui Apaza
        </h5>
        <p class="text-[#536471] dark:text-[#71767B] text-sm">@ypnqh_</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
    <a
      aria-label="Twitter"
      role="link"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="p-2 rounded-full transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-[#0f1419]/10 dark:hover:bg-[#eff3f4]/10 [&>svg]:w-6 fill-[#0f1419] [&>svg]:dark:fill-[#f3f5f7]"
      href="https://twitter.com/ypnqh_"
    >
      <IconX />
    </a>
  </header>
  <main>
    <p
      class="text-[#0F1419] dark:text-[#E7E9EA] line-clamp-4 text-[15px] font-light pb-0.5"
    >
      Hola, soy nuevo en Twitter y no me gustan mucho las redes sociales ðŸ™ƒ
      Estoy buscando conectarme con otros desarrolladores y aprender sobre lo
      Ãºltimo en desarrollo web ðŸ¤—.
    </p>
    <p
      class="pt-1.5 text-[#536471] dark:text-[#71767b] text-sm font-light flex items-center gap-1"
    >
      <span>11:03 am</span>
      <span class="w-[3px] h-[3px] rounded-full bg-[#536471] dark:bg-[#71767b]"
      ></span>
      <span>31 jul. 23</span>
    </p>
  </main>
  <footer
    class="flex gap-5 border-t-[1px] border-[#71767b]/30 pt-4 [&>div>svg]:w-[18px] [&>section>div>svg]:h-[18px]"
  >
    <section class="flex gap-2.5 group cursor-pointer">
      <div class="grid place-items-center place-content-center relative">
        <span
          class="group absolute w-8 h-8 rounded-full group-hover:bg-[#f91880]/[.15]"
        ></span>
        <IconHeart />
      </div>
      <p
        class="text-[#4b5861] dark:text-[#b8c1ca] text-[15px] font-semibold group-hover:text-[#f91880] transition-colors duration-300"
      >
        57
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="flex gap-2.5 group cursor-pointer">
      <div
        class="grid place-items-center place-content-center relative cursor-pointer group"
      >
        <span
          class="absolute w-8 h-8 rounded-full group-hover:bg-[#00ba7c]/10 transition-colors duration-200"
        >
        </span>
        <IconMessageCircle />
      </div>
      <p
        class="text-[#4b5861] dark:text-[#b8c1ca] text-[15px] font-semibold group-hover:text-[#00ba7c] transition-colors duration-300"
      >
        3
      </p>
    </section>
  </footer>
</article>
